<td>1. Log in and inspect session cookie domain attribute<br>2. Access multiple subdomains and verify cookie availability<br>3. Change to explicit subdomain domain (if test environment allows) and observe behavior</td>
<td>Valid creds</td>
<td>When `Domain=.pgl.co.uk` cookie is visible to all subdomains; if domain set to specific subdomain, other subdomains don't receive it</td>
